## Maintenance

When you add, remove, or rename a file in this folder, update **all these indexes** that reference it:

1. `AGENTS.md` reference table at the project root
2. `CLAUDE.md` reference table at the project root (if present)
3. The skill (in `.agents/skills/` or `.claude/skills/`) that points to this doc
4. Any nested `AGENTS.md` files that reference it
5. The file table above

The `writing-docs.md` file has the canonical maintenance checklist.

## For agents without native support

- **GitHub Copilot** - copy the root `AGENTS.md` reference table into `.github/copilot-instructions.md`
- **ChatGPT / other chat agents** - paste the relevant `docs/ai/` file into your conversation when starting work on a matching task
